headline: 2 Stocks Down 30% and 18% to Buy Hand Over Fist
summary: Block's expanding suite of services should allow it to make headway within its vast addressable market.  PayPal's growth opportunities, improved profitability, and strong moat make its outlook attractive.  Naturally, investors want to cash in on this, and two notable companies to consider doing so are Block (NYSE: XYZ) and PayPal (NASDAQ: PYPL).
